<p>Unfortunately the same can't be said of the recursive process.  Clojure can't do much to save us here.  Be forewarned; the code that follows is intended for mature audiences only.  The multiple instances of recursion outside of the loop/recur forms is very likely to induce eye bleeding in any seasoned Clojure programmer:</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
